    dc:creator "Lindner, Mariana Flores; Jr, Milton De Souza Mendonça; Cavalleri, Adriano" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Holopothrips molzi sp. n. (Thysanoptera, Phlaeothripidae): natural history and interactions in Myrtaceae galls" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267475>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267474> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267475>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 10. Holopothrips molzi sp. n. (5) Female body; (6) Ventral view of head and prosternum; (7) Pronotum; (8) Antenna; (9) Mesonotum, metanotum and pelta; (10) Male abdominal sternites V – X, showing the absence of pore plates." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267475/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267474>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Holopothrips molzi sp. n. galls on Myrcia guianensis and its invaders. (1) Green and intact gall; (2) Green and damaged gall (perforated); (3) Dissected gall, showing the immatures of H. molzi (white arrows) and Myrciathrips variabilis (black arrow); (4) Eulophidae larva feeding on H. molzi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

